Bus 003 Device 029: ID 0bda:8771 Realtek Semiconductor Corp. [unknown]

I have a:

	Name: Bluetooth Mouse M557
	Alias: Bluetooth Mouse M557
	Class: 0x00000580 (1408)
	Icon: input-mouse
	Paired: yes
	Bonded: yes
	Trusted: yes
	Blocked: no
