	UUID: PnP Information           (00001200-0000-1000-8000-00805f9b34fb)
	Modalias: usb:v046DpB010d1001

paired to it.

If I leave the computer briefly (minutes, perhaps even a small number
of hours) and return the mouse continues to work correctly.

If I leave the computer for a longer period of time, like say, over
night until the next day, when I try to use the mouse it does not work
immediately.  I can take a few tens of minutes for it to "wake up" and
be functional again.

I didn't have this problem with my old BT dongle.

Any ideas how to resolve this?

